  <!-- Conte√∫do principal -->
  <div class="content">
    <h1>üë®‚Äçüíª Welcome to My GitHub Profile</h1>
    <p>
      Hello! I'm a passionate software developer and data analyst dedicated to creating innovative solutions using code and data.
      My journey combines a strong foundation in software development with data-driven decision-making, focusing on building scalable applications and meaningful insights.
    </p>
